application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Hybrid application for demolition of existing buildings and mixed use redevelopment comprising: 1) Application for detailed planning permission for Class A1 foodstore, a Class A1/A2/A3/D1 retail/community use units, Class C1 hotel, 31 residential units, new public square and associated access, servicing, parking, landscaping and works; & 2)Application for Outline permission with all matters reserved except vehicle access, for up to 185 residential units, up to 430sqm B1, up to 460sqm D1 (nursery), associated access, servicing, parking, landscaping and works.
